{"tid":2142124,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"又一城蘋果員工確診。漠視公眾知情權。","createTime":"2020-08-06T07:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T09:31:32.000Z","uid":90520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"141bef4377276e1451a31e8feaf3efc577d6be71","tid":2142124,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:48:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200806/UT633VO2GI3SCW3LO3BHUMLHSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200806%2FUT633VO2GI3SCW3LO3BHUMLHSQ%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=5e61d402\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200806%2FUT633VO2GI3SCW3LO3BHUMLHSQ%2F&h=81653e22\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200806/UT633VO2GI3SCW3LO3BHUMLHSQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n第三波武漢肺炎在港肆虐，跨國企業的香港員工一樣中招。有香港的蘋果(Apple)員工透露，公司一名員工今日初步確診武漢肺炎，已送院治理。由於該名員工曾經在Apple Store又一城分店工作，該分店即日起會一連停業營業3天，以便清潔消毒，但有員工仍感憂心忡忡。Apple在港其餘5間分店，仍照常營業。<br />\n<br />\n有員工聲稱，蘋果內部原本未有公開事件，有管理人員更涉嫌曾要求員工把有同事確診武漢肺炎一事保密，公司對外只聲稱店舖是暫停營業，被質疑是漠視公眾知情權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1GbcAxq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1GbcAxq.png&h=89a21004&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2f5f6ffacd026efcdd0dc898489c3ef7d28de2e","tid":2142124,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:31:32.000Z","msg":"Bad Apple"}]}